itemDescription: Irish social worker, clown, and magician

wikipedia_page.main: Rosemary or Rosy Gibb (8 November 1942 – 13 July 1997) was an Irish social worker, clown, and magician. She was one of the first women to be accepted into The Magic Circle.

response: *Rosy Gibb, 54, Irish social worker, clown, and magician, cancer.
